    fix(reader): render markdown bold adjustments

    The Reader adjustment flow misclassified long German sentences
    ending with a colon as reusable label prefixes. That produced
    preview rules that changed nothing for blocks containing literal
    Markdown bold markers.

    This adds a dedicated Reader effect for rendering existing
    Markdown strong markers, narrows the label-prefix heuristic, and
    covers the regression in tests and the browser smoke flow.

diff --git a/apps/web/src/components/format-workspace/rule-engine.tsx b/apps/web/src/components/format-workspace/rule-engine.tsx
