//
// PRAGMA foreign_keys must be set outside any transaction (it is a no-op
// inside one per SQLite docs), so we use three separate exec() calls:
// 1. Disable FK enforcement
// 2. DDL work wrapped in BEGIN/COMMIT so a crash between DROP and RENAME
//    cannot leave the database in a half-migrated state
// 3. Re-enable FK enforcement
